  'A classic East Jeju bus day tour covering Ilchul Land, Seongeup Folk Village, Seongsan Ilchulbong, the Haenyeo Show, and Hamdeok Beach. A strong first-time route for travelers who want Jeju’s iconic east-side nature and culture in one day.',
