ing","iconColor":"text-pink-500"},{"name":"Summer","icon":"sun","description":"Hamdeok becomes a stronger crowd-appeal stop. Heat and humidity make Seongsan feel more physically demanding, while Ilchul Land''s shaded caves gain value.","tag":"Lush scenery","bgClass":"bg-summer","iconColor":"text-yellow-500"},{"name":"Autumn","icon":"leaf","description":"Comfortable walking temperatures generally improve overall route feel. Clearer air can lift Seongsan and Hamdeok photo quality.","tag":"Best photo season","bgClass":"bg-autumn","iconColor":"text-orange-500"},{"name":"Winter","icon":"snowflake","description":"Wind exposure matters more at Seongsan, the haenyeo stop, and Hamdeok. The cultural stops become relatively more important for route comfort.","tag":"Weather-sensitive","bgClass":"bg-winter","iconColor":"text-sky-500"}],"faqItems":[{"q":"Is this a good East Jeju tour for first-time visitors?","a":"Yes. It covers several of East Jeju''s best-known highlights in one day and keeps the price lower than a private tour, which makes it a strong first-visit bus option."},{"q":"How difficult is the walking on this route?","a":"Most stops are manageable for average travelers. The one stop that clearly feels more active is Seongsan Ilchulbong, which includes stairs and uphill walking if you go toward the summit."},{"q":"What happens if the haenyeo show is cancelled?","a":"If sea or weather conditions prevent normal operation, the route should switch to Jeju Haenyeo Museum so the cultural logic of the day is preserved."},{"q":"Are admission tickets included?","a":"This JSON is structured for a bus-tour setup where admission is not included unless your checkout configuration says otherwise. Keep the live product setup aligned with your actual offer."}],"reviewsPreview":{"averageRating":4.8,"totalReviews":112,"highlights":[{"label":"Scenery","count":79},{"label":"Guide","count":51},{"label":"Culture","count":42},{"label":"Value","count":47}],"featured":[{"name":"Emma","country":"Australia","rating":5,"comment":"A very satisfying East Jeju route for first-time visitors. Seongsan was the big landmark, but the haenyeo story and Seongeup made the day feel richer than a scenery-only tour.","tripType":"Couple"},{"name":"Michael","country":"United States","rating":4,"comment":"Good value for a bus tour. The Seongsan climb was the hardest part, but the rest of the stops were well spaced and Hamdeok was a nice way to finish.","tripType":"Family"}]},"stickyBooking":{"price":{"amountLabel":"49","currency":"USD","per":"person"}},"matching_profile":{"product_id":"east-jeju-classic-bus-tour","product_type":"bus","route_type":"fixed_route","region_type":"east","region_tags":["jeju_east","seongsan","pyoseon","hamdeok"],"theme_tags":["unesco","folk_village","haenyeo","beach","lava_cave","first_time_friendly","iconic_landmarks","value_route"],"poi_tags":["ilchul_land","seongeup_folk_village","seongsan_ilchulbong","haenyeo_show","hamdeok_beach"],"pace_level":4,"walking_level":3,"scenic_level":5,"photo_level":5,"culture_level":4,"relax_level":3,"first_time_fit":5,"family_fit":4,"senior_fit":3,"couple_fit":5,"active_traveler_fit":4,"one_day_fit":4,"same_day_flight_fit":2,"rain_fit":3,"value_for_money_fit":5,"iconic_landmark_fit":5,"cafe_fit":3,"adult_family_fit":4,"young_kids_fit":3,"senior_active_fit":4,"senior_general_fit":3,"mobility_friendly_fit":2,"stroller_fit":2,"indoor_ratio":32,"weather_sensitivity":3,"local_culture_fit":4,"shopping_fit":2,"storytelling_fit":5,"comfort_level":3,"budget_fit":5,"premium_fit":1,"small_group_fit":1,"private_fit":1,"bus_fit":5,"price_band":"budget","pickup_base":"jeju_city","return_time_band":"17:40-18:20","duration_band":"9h","min_recommended_age":7,"hard_constraints":{"avoidIf":["high_wind_or_rough_sea_alert_on_east_coast","travelers_needing_a_slow_luxury_pace"],"notIdealFor":["very_low_mobility","stroller_heavy_on_steps_or_slopes","travelers_avoiding_stairs"]},"walking_notes":["Overall walking is moderate for a bus to