he haenyeo stop, and Hamdeok are manageable for most travelers.","Seongsan Ilchulbong is the steepest and most physically demanding stop because of stairs and uphill sections.","Comfortable grip shoes are strongly recommended, especially in wet or windy weather."],"keywords":["east jeju bus tour","seongsan ilchulbong hamdeok day tour","jeju folk village and haenyeo tour","ilchul land east jeju tour","best value east jeju bus tour","first time east jeju day trip","hamdeok beach bus day tour","seongeup village seongsan bus tour","jeju haenyeo culture day tour","classic east jeju route"],"synonym_hints":["classic east jeju bus route","east jeju highlights by bus","seongsan hamdeok folk village day","budget-friendly east jeju tour","unesco and beach east jeju day","fixed pickup jeju bus tour"],"profile_version":1,"is_active":true},"matching_metadata":{"matching_schema":"tour_matching_profiles_embedded_v1","embedded_for":["authoring","review","sql_backfill_reference"],"note":"Scores were tuned for a classic East Jeju bus-tour format: very high iconic and storytelling fit, moderate walking overall, and moderate rain resilience because Ilchul Land adds indoor-outdoor balance and the haenyeo stop has a museum fallback, while Seongsan and Hamdeok remain weather-sensitive."},"pickup_dropoff":{"pickupType":"fixed_meeting_points","dropoffType":"fixed_dropoff_points","departure":[{"order":1,"time":"08:30","name":"Ocean Suites Hotel","type":"hotel","note":"Main city pickup point near Tapdong."},{"order":2,"time":"08:45","name":"Jeju Airport, 3rd Floor Gate 3","type":"airport","note":"Departure floor meeting point."},{"order":3,"time":"08:55","name":"Lotte City Hotel Jeju","type":"hotel","note":"Central Jeju City hotel pickup point."},{"order":4,"time":"09:05","name":"Shilla Duty Free Shop","type":"shopping","note":"Popular downtown meeting point."}],"return":[{"order":1,"name":"Ocean Suites Hotel","type":"hotel","note":"Standard city drop-off point."},{"order":2,"name":"Jeju Airport, 3rd Floor Gate 3","type":"airport","note":"Useful for same-day departures; exact stop order may vary."},{"order":3,"name":"Lotte City Hotel Jeju","type":"hotel","note":"Standard city drop-off point."},{"order":4,"name":"Shilla Duty Free Shop","type":"shopping","note":"Standard city drop-off point."},{"order":5,"name":"Dongmun Market","type":"market","note":"Additional downtown drop-off for travelers who want to continue the evening in central Jeju City."}],"notes":["Return usually runs around 17:40–18:20 depending on traffic, weather, and whether the haenyeo show operates normally.","Drop-off order may be adjusted slightly for operational efficiency.","Please arrive at least 10 minutes early at your selected pickup point."]}}'::jsonb
